With GoPledge, you keep 100% of the donations received less the standard online payment processing fees. HOW IT WORKS! Processing Donations GoPledge securely processes all online donations through Stripe. Stripe is a reputable online payment processor that applies a standard credit card processing fee of 2.9% + $0.30 to each donation/transaction. Keeping GoPledge FREE to our schools, organizations, and teams (Optional Platform Fees) In order to allow G

oPledge to offer a FREE top-notch fundraising experience to our schools, organizations and teams, donors will have the option to support GoPledge by adding a voluntary Platform Fee contribution to their donation. Your organization will not incur any charges towards a Platform Fee should donors choose not to contribute. Cash and Check Donations Your school or organization retains 100% of the cash and checks donations received directly from donors. We suggest adding the donations into the system to keep track of all funds and to assist with incentivizing participants for these types of donations

. Timely Payouts We are committed to timely payouts! The funds collected through GoPledge will be processed and sent to your organization via ACH bank deposit after your fundraiser concludes. Whether you’re a donor or an organization running a fundraiser, we’ve got guides, answers, and support to get you going—fast. Got Questions? We’ve Got Answers! Explore the most common things people ask us. What is GoPledge? GoPledge is a FREE online fundraising platform for schools, organizations and teams. Our free and easy-to-use platform offers engaging tools and capabilities, while providing a participant-first experience. Who is GoPledge for? GoPledge i

s for schools, organizations, and teams who are looking for a FREE and easy way to raise money for their cause. How much does GoPledge cost? GoPledge is completely FREE for schools, organizations, and teams to use. There are no upfront costs to begin fundraising and there are no maintenance fees to keep your fundraiser active. GoPledge is donor supported which means donors have the option to make a separate, voluntary contribution towards the GoPledge platform fee. This optional contribution helps keep GoPledge FREE to organizations like you!! It also allows us to keep the site secure and make

updates as new features are needed. Your organization will not incur any charges if the donors choose to not contribute to the optional Platform Fee.Standard credit card fees do apply. For each online transaction, there is a credit card processing fee charged by Stripe, our payment processor. This fee covers the costs associated with processing credit and debit card transactions safely and securely. How do I get started? Just click the “Get Started for FREE” button on our website to create a custom fundraiser for your school, organization or team. Invite your potential participants to join yo

ur fundraiser where they can create their own personalized donation page. They can share their page with friends and family to earn donations for your organization’s cause. How will I receive my funds? Following the conclusion of your fundraiser, the collected funds will be processed and sent to your organization via ACH bank deposit provided all banking information has been received from your organization and is accurate. Can we accept cash and check donations? Yes! Your school or organization retains 100% of the cash and check donations received directly from donors. How do I contact someone

on the GoPledge team? LINK TO THE CONTACT PAGE Our fundraising experts are here to help! Simply fill out the contact form on our website or give us a call at 346-515-5722. You can also email us at info@GoPledge.com. How do I learn more about GoPledge? LINK TO LAURIE’S HUBSPOT MEETING LINK Our website is full of great information about how GoPledge can help your school, organization or team raise funds.
